Usage: reset_ccopt_routing_state [-help] [-excluded <nets>] [-no_delete_routes]
                                 [-reset_preroutes]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-excluded <nets>     # list of excluded nets ((net)+, optional)
-no_delete_routes    # do not remove clock routes (bool, optional)
-reset_preroutes     # Reset the status of pre-routes (bool, optional)